(43, 'Sayeman Beach Resort', 'Luxury Hotel', 'Bangladesh', 'Marine Drive, Kolatoli, Cox\'s Bazar Sadar, Cox\'s Bazar', '+8809610777888', 'reservation@sayemanresort.com', 'Modern luxury hotel with stunning sea views, infinity pool, and fine dining. Located directly on Kolatoli beach front.', 'Wi-Fi,Parking,Restaurant,AC,Swimming Pool,Gym,Sea View,Conference Hall,Airport Shuttle,Family Rooms', 'images/hotels/sayeman_beach_resort.jpeg', 12500.00, 5, '2025-06-05 10:05:43'),
